OL,4,Chospital after norovirus cases fall
OL,6,FThe hospital is reminding the public
OL,7,Fabout the importance of reducing
OL,8,Fcontact with others if they are
OL,9,Fexperiencing symptoms of norovirus.
OL,11,FSymptoms of norovirus include feeling
OL,12,Fsick, being sick, diarrhoea, a high
OL,13,Ftemperature, a headache, tummy pain
OL,14,Fbody aches and pains.
OL,16,FAnyone with norovirus is being urged
OL,17,Fnot to visit hospitals or care homes
OL,18,Funtil they are free from symptoms for
OL,19,Fat least 48 hours and to only use the
OL,20,FEmergency Department for genuine
OL,21,Fmedical emergencies.
